{"tid":1861904,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"賀一誠稱國家缺口罩，現時再要求供應非好事，轉而買起葡萄牙口罩供澳 同時強制要求巴士上戴口罩","createTime":"2020-02-04T10:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T17:49:23.000Z","uid":133680,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8d9a5faa7420b36684781635f3e875c7e131a429","tid":1861904,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:52:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506560-20200204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506560-20200204.htm&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=2cd689fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506560-20200204.htm&h=28a7d49c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506560-20200204.htm</a><br />\n澳門政府因應新型肺炎疫情，決定暫停博彩業及相關娛樂事業半個月。<br />\n<br />\n澳門行政長官賀一誠表示，不是有錢就買到口罩，會不惜代價將口罩運到澳門，形容「葡萄牙都已經俾我哋買哂，無哂口罩」。他說，2000萬個口罩供應肯定無問題，亦足夠用一個月，而目前國家缺乏口罩，澳門作為國家一份子，再向國家要求供應口罩，並非很好的事。<br />\n<br />\n賀一誠又說，市民可能覺得坐交通工具戴口罩會不方便，但現時不是實行便民措施，而是希望大家感到麻煩，不要出街。<br />\n<br />\n他又強調，澳門不會封關，呼籲民眾不要搶物資，又說是「睇電視先知道」香港政府暫停碼頭口岸，澳門封閉賭場的決定，未有事先與香港商討。"},{"pid":"46baf1fa01e6e2c4bfe3b4c962e92031801522e9","tid":1861904,"uid":313341,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:55:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0130c73b01691b13eb405bfce36d063f670761df","tid":1861904,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb694533b9000de0c9e03c182fd135d2b073fc0","tid":1861904,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:55:45.000Z","msg":"2舊都係屎<br />\n<br />\n邊舊臭D"},{"pid":"e9df841ade90e0a2b92a264b7342ffe97687ce05","tid":1861904,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195f4e9810c2643061bde1ef557d6de5372d4ec1","tid":1861904,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:09:02.000Z","msg":"想知葡萄牙產量有幾多"},{"pid":"03c47f83e556252d27fcc80146754aa86d9a04d7","tid":1861904,"uid":64694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"195f4e9810c2643061bde1ef557d6de5372d4ec1","tid":1861904,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:09:02.000Z","msg":"想知葡萄牙產量有幾多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:20:40.000Z","msg":"可能得一個，之後就話葡萄牙嘅口罩已經俾我哋買晒，其他嗰19999999已經向國家拎咗，再向國家拎就唔係咁好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feddc0d26c98363a63c743c0c5033eb9f495fe33","tid":1861904,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:34:49.000Z","msg":"他說，2000萬個口罩供應肯定無問題，亦足夠用一個月，而目前國家缺乏口罩，澳門作為國家一份子，再向國家要求供應口罩，並非很好的事。<br />\n<br />\n又說是「睇電視先知道」香港政府暫停碼頭口岸，澳門封閉賭場的決定，未有事先與香港商討。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又暗串777"},{"pid":"f26304fa6b730bd4262985df87630b9b3c728178","tid":1861904,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T12:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a079af9e9dbe64aebe5c626a668db45a8a6b3540","tid":1861904,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"串到，好正"},{"pid":"58345bfd6f36c919e0205d22c4647f0e9d7b5a95","tid":1861904,"uid":272614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T12:12:43.000Z","msg":"澳門咁細需求都唔算好大，不過話時話呢個殖民國家真係唔話得"},{"pid":"1f66f63ddaabc90bb7356c78d088363bd324ad93","tid":1861904,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T12:19:48.000Z","msg":"國家捐左幾十萬個俾賓賓 點會缺口罩 賀特係咪尋釁滋事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43054b9573a86b5da3ee23b2ce55908714114f42","tid":1861904,"uid":32